---
import TestimonialsCard from "../../components/TestimonialsCard.astro";
---

<section class="w-screen p-2 text-[#e2e4ec] border-b">
  <h1 class="text-4xl text-center font-bold">Testimonials</h1>
  <div
    class="md:w-[900px] mx-auto mt-4 flex gap-2 justify-center overflow-hidden"
  >
    <div class="flex gap-2 animate">
      <TestimonialsCard
        title="Relieved Homeowner"
        text="I was struggling to maintain my pool until I found this service. They took charge and made my pool look brand new. Now, I can relax and enjoy the water worry-free. Thank you for your exceptional work!"
        photo="/testimonials/01.webp"
        author="Sarah L."
      />
      <TestimonialsCard
        title="Happy Pool Owner"
        text="Absolutely thrilled with the transformation! Our pool went from cloudy to crystal clear in no time. The team's professionalism and attention to detail are unmatched. Highly recommend their service!"
        photo="/testimonials/02.webp"
        author="John T."
      />
      <TestimonialsCard
        title="Impressed Customer"
        text="From the first consultation to the regular maintenance, I've been impressed. Their dedication to not just cleaning but also educating pool owners is commendable. The results speak for themselvesâ€”my pool has never been better!"
        photo="/testimonials/03.webp"
        author="David R."
      />
      <TestimonialsCard
        title="Satisfied Customer"
        text="A friend recommended this service, and I'm so glad I listened. The team is reliable, knowledgeable, and genuinely cares about the health of my pool. I've found my go-to for all things pool-related!"
        photo="/testimonials/04.webp"
        author="Emma S."
      />
      <TestimonialsCard
        title="Delighted Pool Enthusiast"
        text="I've used various pool services before, but none come close to the quality I experienced here. They don't just clean; they rejuvenate! My pool is now the highlight of my backyard, thanks to their consistent, top-notch service."
        photo="/testimonials/05.webp"
        author="Michael H."
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes testimonials_animate {
    0% {
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
    100% {
      transform: translateX(50%);
    }
  }

  .animate {
    animation: testimonials_animate 15s alternate-reverse infinite ease;
  }

  .animate:hover {
    animation-play-state: paused;
  }
</style>
